                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12973327" author="deraj123" created="Mon, 20 Dec 2010 19:34:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixes the leak by closing the ResultSet on each iteration of the loop, and only ever creating a single PreparedStatement.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
